OL,3,CNI paediatric services 'unsustainable'
OL,4,Cand in need of change
OL,6,FA review of paediatric waiting times
OL,7,Fin Northern Ireland shows the number
OL,8,Fof children waiting for outpatient
OL,9,Fappointments has reached "an all-time
OL,10,Fhigh".
OL,12,FA report from the Royal College of
OL,13,FPaediatrics and Child Health (RCPCH)
OL,14,Frevealed that between June 2016 and
OL,15,FJune 2023, there was a 172.6% overall
OL,16,Fincrease of children waiting for a
OL,17,Ffirst outpatient appointment.
OL,19,FThere was an increase of 21.3% for
OL,20,Fthose waiting over 52 weeks in the
OL,21,Fsame period.
