OL,3,CNI paediatric services 'unsustainable'
OL,4,Cand in need of change
OL,6,FDr Ray Nethercott, RCPCH Ireland
OL,7,FOfficer, has described it as a
OL,8,F"catastrophe for children".
OL,10,F"The upward trajectory of outpatient
OL,11,Fwaiting times for paediatrics has
OL,12,Fcontinued to increase year on year
OL,13,Fsince 2016, reaching an all-time high
OL,14,Fin 2023," says Dr Nethercott.
OL,16,F"This is unsustainable and real
OL,17,Fsystemic change is needed to turn this
OL,18,Fcurve."
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G2/8
