OL,6,FAccording to the report, in June 2016
OL,7,Fthe total number of ongoing waits was
OL,8,F8,170, while in June 2023 it had risen
OL,9,Fto 22,272.
OL,11,FIn terms of the difference between
OL,12,F2022 and 2023, the figure rose from
OL,13,F18,179 total ongoing waits to 22,272,
OL,14,Fwhich is an increase of 22.5%.
OL,16,FWhen looking at the group with the
OL,17,Flongest ongoing waits - over 52 weeks
OL,18,F- there were 578 ongoing waits in June
OL,19,F2016 compared to 6,326 in June 2023.
