OL,6,FPatients waiting over 52 weeks made up
OL,7,F7.1% of total waits in the quarter
OL,8,Fending June 2016, while in the quarter
OL,9,Fending June 2023, they made up 28.4%
OL,10,Fof total waits.
OL,12,F"We know that NI has faced
OL,13,Finsurmountable pressures within Health
OL,14,Fand Social Care, but the current
OL,15,Fconfiguration of paediatrics is not
OL,16,Fworking," says Dr Nethercott.
OL,18,F"It has been pointed out by numerous
OL,19,Fstakeholders, including the Children's
OL,20,FCommissioner that NI has the lowest
OL,21,Fspend on children's services in the UK.
