OL,6,F"In health, the funding allocations
OL,7,Fare much less clear and do not adhere
OL,8,Fto the five child rights principles
OL,9,Ffor public budgeting i.e.
OL,10,Feffectiveness, efficiency, equity,
OL,11,Ftransparency and sustainability.
OL,13,F"Nonetheless, working together, to
OL,14,Freconfigure how we deliver child
OL,15,Fcentred health care, in the right
OL,16,Fplace, at the right time, by the right
OL,17,Fpeople, we can better serve our
OL,18,Finfants, children and young people."
