OL,6,FIn a statement, the Department of
OL,7,FHealth said "tackling lengthy waiting
OL,8,Ftimes is a key priority" and that it
OL,9,F"requires sustainable and recurrent
OL,10,Ffunding".
OL,12,FA spokesperson continued: "This report
OL,13,Fdemonstrates that we must do
OL,14,Feverything we can to improve outcomes
OL,15,Ffor children and young people.
OL,17,F"We recognise the pandemic and ongoing
OL,18,Fresource constraints have exacerbated
OL,19,Fexisting pressures on children's
OL,20,Fservices and have adversely impacted
OL,21,Fchildren's health and wellbeing.
