OL,6,F"The Child Health Partnership, and the
OL,7,Frecently established Programme Board,
OL,8,Fare currently working to rebuild and
OL,9,Freconfigure services following the
OL,10,Fpandemic.
OL,12,F"Tackling lengthy waiting times is a
OL,13,Fkey priority. It is, undoubtedly, a
OL,14,Flong-term issue that requires
OL,15,Fsustainable and recurrent funding,
OL,16,Fworkforce development and system-wide
OL,17,Ftransformation.
